                            <comment id="14679164" author="snazy" created="Sun, 9 Aug 2015 14:57:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;(as discussed offline&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; I think a good choice for the thread pool size would be the number of CPUs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
